treeAggregateExpression.name: QRi
treeAggregateExpression.label: 期望变化率
treeAggregateExpression.description: 热量期望变化率QRi=自己的供热不平衡率+逐级父级的供热不平衡率

treeNodeExpressions.name: Ri
treeNodeExpressions.label: 供热不平衡率
treeNodeExpressions.description: Ri=(a-b)/a,其中：a为实际供热占比，b为预测供热占比
treeNodeExpressions.expression: if(instantaneous_heat[1] != 0 && vsum(instantaneousHeatLine1) != 0, instantaneousHeatLine1[1] * vsum(instantaneous_heat) / vsum(instantaneousHeatLine1) / instantaneous_heat[1] - 1 , 0)

conditions.QRi_normalization: if(a - b == 0 || QRi_MAX - QRi_MIN == 0, 0, (QRi - QRi_MAX) * (a - b) / (QRi_MAX - QRi_MIN) + a)

nodes.name: 换热站6组条件最终结果

conditions.condition: Ri_enable == 1 && control_enable == 1 && valve_enable == 1 && pressure_enable == 1 && temperature_enable == 1 && instantaneousFlow_enable == 1 && all_enable == 1

conditions.threeMin_condition: if(timestamp_Change_enable == 1 || Vi_control_last - runOpening_last == 0, 0, (Vi_control_last - runOpening) / (Vi_control_last - runOpening_last) > percent3)
conditions.fourMin_condition: if(timestamp_Change_enable == 1 || instantaneousFlowLine1_last == 0, 0, (instantaneousFlowLine1 - instantaneousFlowLine1_last) / instantaneousFlowLine1_last * QRi_last > percent4)
conditions.tenMin_condition: if(timestamp_Change_enable == 1 || supplyWaterTemperatureLine2_last == 0, 0, (supplyWaterTemperatureLine2 - supplyWaterTemperatureLine2_last) / supplyWaterTemperatureLine2_last * QRi_last > percent10)
